<UniverseScene>

Handles camera, system vs focus state.

Renders <PlanetDots> for all repos in system mode (instanced, cheap).

Renders <HeroPlanet> when one repo is selected (single high-detail planet).

<PlanetDots>

Instanced mesh/material: position, scale, colour; hover/click to select.

